@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
actor Customer
participant Frontend as FE
participant Backend as API
participant "Coin Service" as Coins
participant Database as DB
actor Seller

Customer -> FE: Submit Review (Rating, Comment, Photos)
FE -> API: Process Review Request
API -> DB: Verify Order Completed & Unreviewed
DB --> API: Verification OK
API -> DB: Save Review
API -> Coins: Calculate Reward (e.g., +100 Coins)
Coins -> DB: Add Coins to Customer Wallet
Coins --> API: Reward Processed
API --> FE: Return Success & Coins Earned

FE --> Customer: Display "Review Submitted! +100 Coins"
API --> Seller: Notify "New Product Review"

Seller -> FE: View Review
Seller -> API: Submit Reply to Review
API -> DB: Save Reply
API --> Customer: Notify "Seller replied to your review"
@enduml
